mitre_defs.description:
This dictionary represents the relationship between MITRE attack tactics and techniques.
Each tactic is as a key and the value is a list of associated techniques or sub-techniques.
For example: "mitre_defs": {"TA0007": ["T1007", "T1033"], "TA0002": ["T1037.001"]}

